The two are also embroiled in a dangerous mystery that involves a sexy customs agent which includes more excitement and danger than they anticipated.The friends get involved in a case when two U.S. customs agents are murdered after investigating an illegal counterfeiting scam led by Ricky Tan, one of the most powerful Triad gangsters and an enemy of Lee's.

movies.title: Shallow Hal
movies.synopsis: Shallow Hal is a superficial skirt chaser who, after a mind-altering experience with a self-help guru, doesn't realise that his gorgeous girlfriend is actually a 300-pound not-so-hottie. Meanwhile, Hal's playboy pal Mauricio is determined to break the spell before someone gets ... squashed! Packed with loads of laughs and nonstop fun, it's the biggest love story ever told.

movies.title: You Don't Mess with the Zohan
movies.matchTitle: You Don't Mess with the Zohan
movies.synopsis: The Zohan is the finest counterterrorist agent the Israeli army has. That is, until he fakes his death and travels to Manhattan to live his dream as a hairdresser. Now this skilled fighting machine who used to clip bad guys is out to prove he can make the cut as a top stylist. All goes silky smooth until his cover is blown when he's recognised by a Palestinian cab driver. Now, the Zohan must fight to live a peaceful new life in New York in this razor-sharp action-packed comedy.

movies.title: The Watch
movies.synopsis: Four everyday suburban guys come together as an excuse to escape their humdrum lives one night a week. But when they accidentally discover that their town has become overrun with aliens posing as ordinary suburbanites, they have no choice but to save their neighbourhood, and the world, from total extermination.

movies.title: Galaxy Quest
movies.synopsis: For four years, the courageous crew of the NSEA Protector set off on thrilling and often dangerous missions in space - and then their series was cancelled. Now, 20 years later, aliens under attack mistake the Galaxy Quest television transmissions for historical documents and beam up the crew of has-been actors to save the universe. With no script, no director and no clue, the actors must turn in the performances of their lives.

movies.title: Bruce Almighty
movies.synopsis: Bruce is a reporter who blames God for his woes, until God dares him to do a better job for a day.

movies.title: Get Hard
movies.synopsis: Sentenced to hard time in prison, a weak-willed millionaire hires a gangster to harden him up. But when the gangster turns out to be a lily-livered do-gooder, both are in for a shock.

movies.title: Extremities
movies.synopsis: A woman is attacked by a would-be rapist, and manages to escape but the man has taken her wallet, and she lives in mortal fear that he will seek her out. Her nightmare comes true when a strange man knocks on her door one day while she is alone. But the sadistic attacker doesn't count on her being ready for him.

movies.title: Looper
movies.synopsis: In the futuristic action-thriller, time travel will be invented - but it will be illegal and only available on the black market. When the mob wants to get rid of someone, they will send their target 30 years into the past, where a "looper" - a hired gun, like Joe - is waiting to mop up. Joe is getting rich and life is good, until the day the mob decides to "close the loop", sending back Joe's future self for assassination.

movies.title: Spring Breakers
movies.synopsis: After a spring break splurge, four bikini-clad criminals are bailed out by a gangster who introduces them to a world of drugs, danger, and death.

movies.title: Gone Baby Gone
movies.synopsis: When four-year-old Amanda McCready disappears from her home and the police make little headway in solving the case, the girl's aunt, Beatrice McCready hires two private detectives, Patrick Kenzie and Angie Gennaro. The detectives freely admit that they have little experience with this type of case, but the family wants them for two reasons, they're not cops and they know the tough neighbourhood in which they all live. As the case progresses, Kenzie and Gennaro face drug dealers, gangs and paedophiles. When they are about to solve the case, they are faced with a moral dilemma that tears them apart.

movies.title: Inside Man
movies.synopsis: A tough cop, a clever bank robber and a power broker fuel a dangerous game of cat-and-mouse full of hidden agendas and explosive surprises. Get ready for heart-pounding suspense that will keep you guessing until the very end.

movies.title: Misery
movies.synopsis: When a successful romantic novelist, Paul Sheldon, has his life saved by his No.1 fan, he lives to regret it. When Ann Wilkes discovers that her favourite character, Misery Chastain, has been killed off in his latest novel, she'll do anything to make sure he brings her back to life. Now Paul Sheldon must write as if his life depended on it - because now it does.

movies.title: RocknRolla
movies.synopsis: When a Russian mobster orchestrates a crooked land deal, millions of dollars are up for grabs, drawing in the entire London underworld into a feeding frenzy.

movies.title: Let Me In
movies.synopsis: Abby is a mysterious 12-year-old who moves next door to Owen, a social outcast who is viciously bullied at school. In his loneliness, Owen forms a profound bond with his new neighbour but he cant help noticing that Abby is like no one he has met before. As a string of grisly murders grips his wintry New Mexico town, Owen has to confront the reality that this seemingly innocent girl is hiding a dark secret.

movies.title: Paranormal Activity
movies.synopsis: A young couple suspects that their house is haunted by a malevolent entity, so they set up video surveillance to capture evidence of what happens at night as they sleep.

movies.title: Moon
movies.synopsis: Astronaut Sam Bell is living on the far side of the moon, completing a three-year contract with Lunar Industries to mine Earth's primary source of energy, Helium-3. It is a lonely job, made harder by a broken satellite that allows no live communications home. Taped messages are all Sam can send and receive. Thankfully, his time on the moon is nearly over, and Sam will be reunited with his wife, Tess, and their three-year-old daughter, Eve, in only a few short weeks.

movies.title: Killer Assistant
movies.synopsis: A magazine editor's life and career begin to unravel after she takes on a new assistant with secret motives of his own.

movies.title: The Bone Collector
movies.synopsis: A murderer is loose on the streets of Manhattan. A diabolical killer whose brutal slayings leave a trail of cryptic messages hidden at the scene of the crime. Clues which only a brilliant mind can interpret. Lincoln Rhyme is a gifted but disabled detective who is assigned to the case as the city becomes gripped with fear. Amelia Donaghy is a feisty, street-smart policewoman, who together with Lincoln, must go inside the mind of this terrifying madman and defeat him at his own game.

movies.title: Black Sea
movies.synopsis: A rogue submarine captain pulls together a misfit crew to go after a sunken treasure rumoured to be lost in the depths of the Black Sea. As greed and desperation take control on board their claustrophobic vessel, the increasing uncertainty of the mission causes the men to turn on each other to fight for their own survival.

movies.title: Dark Water
movies.synopsis: Dahlia Williams is starting a new life; with a new job and new apartment, she's determined to put her relationship with her estranged husband behind her and devote herself to raising her daughter, Ceci. But when the strained separation disintegrates into a bitter custody battle, mysterious noises, persistent leaks of dark water, and strange happenings in the apartment cause her imagination to run wild. As Dahlia frantically searches for the links between the riddles, the dark water seems to close around her. But no matter what it is that's out there, Dahlia will stop at nothing to find it.

movies.title: The Da Vinci Code
movies.synopsis: A Harvard professor implicated in a murder must unravel an ancient code to expose the greatest conspiracy in history.

movies.title: Inferno
movies.synopsis: The famous symbologist Robert Langdon wakes up in an Italian hospital with amnesia and finds himself the target of a manhunt. Langdon teams up with Sienna Brooks; a doctor he hopes will help him recover his memories. Together, they race across Europe and against the clock to stop a virus that would wipe out half of the world's population.

movies.title: Changing Lanes
movies.synopsis: One wrong turn deserves another. Affluent Wall Street lawyer Gavin Banek and recovering alcoholic Doyle Gipson are both on their way to vital court hearings, when they get involved in a fender bender accident with each other on New York's FDR Drive. In a rush, Banek leaves the scene without doing things by the book, but he leaves behind an important document. Stranded, Gipson is late for a custody hearing, and so begins a cruel game of one-upmanship between the men.

movies.title: The Taking of Pelham 1 2 3
movies.synopsis: Walter Garber is a New York City subway dispatcher whose ordinary day is thrown into chaos by an audacious crime: the hijacking of a subway train. Ryder, the criminal mastermind behind the hijacking and leader of a highly-armed gang of four, threatens to execute the train's passengers unless a large ransom is paid within one hour. As the tension mounts beneath his feet, Garber employs his vast knowledge of the subway system in a battle to outwit Ryder and save the hostages. But there's one riddle Garber can't solve: even if the thieves get the money, how can they possibly escape?

movies.title: I Am Legend
movies.synopsis: Robert Neville is a brilliant scientist, but even he could not contain the terrible virus that was unstoppable, incurable, and man-made. Somehow immune, Neville is now the last human survivor in what is left of New York City and maybe the world. For three years, Neville has faithfully sent out daily radio messages, desperate to find any other survivors who might be out there. But he is not alone. Mutant victims of the plague - The Infected - lurk in the shadows, watching Neville's every move, waiting for him to make a fatal mistake. Perhaps mankind's last, best hope, Neville is driven by only one remaining mission: to find a way to reverse the effects of the virus using his own immune blood. But he knows he is outnumbered ... and quickly running out of time.

movies.title: The Purge
movies.synopsis: If you could commit any crime without consequences, what would you do? This is an inventive thriller that dares you to survive the most dangerous night in America - the Purge - when all crime is legal for 12 hours. When an intruder breaks into James Sandin's gated community during the yearly lockdown, he begins a sequence of events that threatens to tear a family apart. Now, it is up to James, his wife, Mary, and their kids to make it through the night without turning into the monsters from whom they hide.

movies.title: The Enemy Within
movies.synopsis: An officer with the Joint Chiefs of Staffs suspects that his boss, a high-ranking general, is plotting a military coup to topple the weak US president.

movies.title: The Ghost Writer
movies.synopsis: A successful ghostwriter agrees to complete the memoirs of a former British prime minister, but the project seems suspicious, not least because the previous writer died in an unfortunate accident.

movies.title: Red Eye
movies.synopsis: Lisa Reisert hates to fly, but the terror that awaits her on the night flight to Miami has nothing to do with a fear of flying. Moments after take-off, Lisa's charming seat mate, Jackson, menacingly reveals the real reason he's on board: He is an operative in a plot to kill a rich and powerful businessman ... and Lisa is the key to its success. If she refuses to cooperate, her own father will be killed by an assassin awaiting a call from Jackson. Trapped within the confines of a jet at 30,000 feet, Lisa has nowhere to run and no way to summon help without endangering her father, her fellow passengers and her own life. As the miles tick by, Lisa knows she is running out of time as she desperately looks for a way to thwart her ruthless captor and stop a terrible murder.

movies.title: The Queen Of Sin
movies.synopsis: For Posy, life has been smooth sailing. She's got Tom, her doctor fiance, whom she's dated since a teenager; her burgeoning career as a medical illustrator and a side hobby as a visual artist. But after a chance encounter with a handsome, worldly businessman named Jack, Posy begins to see her shell crack. She finds him mysterious and he finds her charming, and for Posy it is an opportunity to try on confidence for size. Posy is reluctant to take it any further than petty flirting, but her cousin Laura, her complete opposite, pushes for one last fling before settling down with Tom, the only man she has ever been with. Posy's growing desire to break free allows her to exercise her inner self with Jack, an alter ego she's created called the Queen of Sin. Little does Posy know, as she's being swept up by Jack, she's really making a deal with the devil.

movies.title: John Q
movies.synopsis: John Q Archibald is an ordinary man whose life revolves around his family. His wife Denise and young son Michael are his world. But when Michael falls seriously ill and needs an emergency heart transplant operation that John Q can't afford and his health insurance won't cover, he vows to do whatever it will take to keep his son alive. With time and options running out, a desperate gamble becomes his only hope - he takes the hospital emergency room hostage.

movies.title: State of Play
movies.synopsis: When D.C. Reporter Cal McCaffrey is assigned to investigate the murder of an assistant to an up-and-coming politician, he uncovers a conspiracy that threatens to bring down the nation's power structures. In a town of spin-doctors and wealthy power brokers, he will discover one truth: when fortunes are at stake, no one's integrity, love or life is safe.

movies.title: The Score
movies.synopsis: An ageing thief plans to retire when his friend and a young, aggressive crim convinces him into doing one last heist - steal a valuable French sceptre worth millions, but who will be double crossed out of their share?

movies.title: Conspiracy Theory
movies.synopsis: A crackpot New York cabbie lands in trouble after his conspiracy magazine attracts the interest of shady government heavies and leads to five unexplained murders.

movies.title: Sherlock Holmes
movies.synopsis: Sherlock Holmes has always been the smartest man in the room - until now. There is a new criminal mastermind at large, Professor Moriarty, and not only is he Holmes' intellectual equal, but his capacity for evil, coupled with a complete lack of conscience, may actually give him an advantage over the renowned detective. When the Crown Prince of Austria is found dead, the evidence, as construed by Inspector Lestrade, points to suicide, but Sherlock Holmes deduces that the prince has been the victim of murder, a murder that is only one piece of a larger and much more portentous puzzle, designed by Professor Moriarty. The cunning Moriarty is always one step ahead of Holmes as he spins a web of death and destruction, all part of a greater plan that, if he succeeds, will change the course of history.

movies.title: Unknown
movies.synopsis: Dr Martin Harris awakens after a car accident in Berlin to discover that his wife suddenly doesn't recognise him and another man has assumed his identity. Ignored by disbelieving authorities and hunted by mysterious assassins, he finds himself alone, tired and on the run. Aided by an unlikely ally, Harris plunges into a deadly mystery forcing him to question his sanity, his identity and just how far he's willing to go to uncover the truth.

movies.title: Taken
movies.synopsis: An ex-secret agent turns Paris inside out when his teenage daughter is kidnapped by European slave traders.

movies.title: Taken 2
movies.synopsis: Bryan Mills, a retired CIA agent with a 'particular set of skills' who stopped at nothing to save his daughter Kim from kidnappers. When the father of one of the villains Bryan killed swears revenge, and takes Bryan and his wife hostage in Istanbul, Bryan enlists Kim to help them escape. Bryan then employs his unique tactics to get his family to safety and systematically take out the kidnappers, one by one.

movies.title: Species
movies.synopsis: When a beautiful human-alien hybrid escapes from observation, scientist Xavier Fitch dispatches a crew of experts to find her before she is able to fulfil her horrific purpose: to mate with unsuspecting men and produce offspring that could destroy mankind. As her deadly biological clock ticks rapidly, Fitch and his team are hurled into a desperate battle in which the fate of humanity itself hangs in the balance!

movies.title: Species II
movies.synopsis: The son of a senator and the first man on Mars, Patrick Ross, returns home a hero, a champion and a carrier of the deadliest known DNA in the universe. Something is taking over his body, a strain of alien DNA that has been to earth before. Now, the only chance for the human race is the woman who tried to destroy it. Dr Laura Baker has recreated the alien species from a frozen lab embryo that is identical to Sil in every respect except that her alien traits are dormant. Eve is half human. However, when another of her kind contacts her, she is challenged emotionally. Her loyalty is to man, but her instinct is to mate.

movies.title: Species III
movies.synopsis: Sara, the daughter of Eve, begins her mission to mate with humans, while a specialist military team hunt her down to kill her before it's too late.

movies.title: Species IV: The Awakening
movies.synopsis: A scientist, Dr Holander, takes his niece Miranda to Mexico in an attempt to reverse the effects of the alien DNA he used to create her.

movies.title: Unbreakable
movies.synopsis: On a day that starts out as any other, David Dunn becomes the sole survivor of a catastrophic train wreck. Finding himself miraculously unharmed, he begins an emotional journey to understand the meaning of the miracle in his life. On his path of self-discovery, David meets Elijah Price, an eccentric stranger who is convinced that David possesses an extraordinary gift. Reflecting on Elijah's theory, David realises that he has never been sick, never broken a bone and never been harmed. Slowly, David begins to discover the shocking truth behind Elijah's supernatural explanation for David's amazing existence.

movies.title: 25th Hour
movies.synopsis: Monty Brogan is an educated, charming young man who once faced a bright future, but that changes when he is convicted of selling heroin and sentenced to seven years in a federal penitentiary. Twenty-four hours before beginning his jail sentence, Monty prowls the streets of New York City with his girlfriend and his two best friends, re-examining his past choices, but as the final hour slips by, Monty seizes one last chance to change his future and enacts a shocking and disturbing plan that will seal his destiny in the 25th hour.

movies.title: The Day the Earth Stood Still
movies.matchTitle: The Day the Earth Stood Still
movies.synopsis: Klaatu is an otherworldly being whose arrival on Earth triggers an unstoppable series of events that threaten all of mankind. In a desperate attempt to save humanity, governments and scientists race to unravel the mystery behind the visitors appearance. When a woman and her young stepson find themselves embroiled in the alien's plan, they become the world's only hope to stave off apocalyptic annihilation.

movies.title: The Insider
movies.synopsis: This film keeps you on the edge of your seat as it recounts the chain of events that pitted an ordinary man against big business, and ultimately dragged people into the fight of their lives. Two men crusade together for a public health issue charged with emotion. And it's not long before they both find out just how badly the corporate giants want to save their bottom lines.

movies.title: The Commuter
movies.synopsis: A businessman is caught up in a criminal conspiracy during his daily commute home. Now a hardworking life insurance salesman and a caring family man, the former police officer, Michael MacCauley, has taken the commuter rail to New York for the past ten years. But, unexpectedly, things will take a turn for the worse, when on one of his daily journeys, the cryptic passenger, Joanna, makes Michael a generous and tempting offer to locate a single commuter or face grave consequences. Is this a sick joke, or is this indeed a serious situation? As Michael races against the clock to solve this wicked conundrum, everyone aboard is a suspect, in a deal where there's definitely more than meets the eye. Can he decide in time who's the one?

movies.title: Cape Fear
movies.synopsis: Fourteen years after being imprisoned, vicious psychopath Max Cady emerges with a single-minded mission: to seek revenge on his attorney Sam Bowden. Cady becomes a terrifying presence as he menacingly circles Bowden's increasingly unstable family. Realising he is legally powerless to protect his beautiful wife Leigh and his troubled teenage daughter Danielle, Sam resorts to unorthodox measures which lead to an unforgettable showdown on Cape Fear.

movies.title: Inglourious Basterds
movies.synopsis: As war rages in Europe, a Nazi-scalping squad of American soldiers, known to their enemy as 'The Basterds', is on a daring mission to take down the leaders of the Third Reich.

movies.title: The Usual Suspects
movies.synopsis: Held in an LA interrogation room, Verbal Kint attempts to convince the Feds that a mythic crime lord not only exists, but was also responsible for drawing him and his four partners into a multimillion-dollar heist that ended with an explosion in San Pedro harbour, leaving few survivors. As Kint lures his interrogators into the incredible story of this crime lord's almost supernatural prowess, so, too, will you be taken in by a story that is completely captivating from beginning to end.

movies.title: Gothika
movies.synopsis: A brilliant and respected criminal psychologist, Dr Miranda Grey is an expert at knowing what is rational. Under the direction of her husband, Miranda treats dangerously disturbed patients at the Woodward Penitentiary for Women. But Miranda's life is thrust into terrifying jeopardy after a cryptic encounter with a mysterious young girl leads to a nightmare beyond her wildest imagination.

movies.title: Hereafter
movies.synopsis: George is a blue-collar American who has a special connection to the afterlife. On the other side of the world, Marie, a French journalist, has a near-death experience that shakes her reality. When Marcus, a London schoolboy, loses the person closest to him, he desperately needs answers. Each on a path in search of the truth, their lives will intersect, forever changed by what they believe might - or must - exist in the Hereafter.

movies.title: Slender Man
movies.synopsis: In a small town in Massachusetts, four high school girls perform a ritual in an attempt to debunk the lore of SLENDER MAN. When one of the girls goes mysteriously missing, they begin to suspect that she is, in fact, HIS latest victim.

movies.title: The Talented Mr. Ripley
movies.synopsis: Tom, a calculating young man, believes it's better to be a fake somebody than a real nobody. Opportunity knocks in the form of a wealthy US shipbuilder who hires Tom to travel to Italy to bring back his playboy son, Dickie. Ripley worms his way into the idyllic lives of Dickie and his girlfriend, plunging into a daring scheme of duplicity, lies and murder.

movies.title: Tinker Tailor Soldier Spy
movies.synopsis: A masterful adaptation of John le Carre's bestselling novel that redefined the spy thriller. At the height of the Cold War, a precarious operation goes deadly wrong, and the head of British Intelligence wonders if a double agent is leaking vital secrets. Brought out of retirement to expose the potential mole, master spy George Smiley is the only one who can be trusted to expose one of their own. Or can he? As the emotional and physical tolls mount on the high-ranking suspects, Smiley will be forced into the ultimate international spy game where everyone's motives are in question.

movies.title: Out of Sight
movies.synopsis: Meet Jack Foley, the most successful bank robber in the country. On the day he busts out of jail, he finds himself stealing something far more precious than money: Karen Sisco's heart. She's smart, she's sexy, and, unfortunately for Jack, she's a federal marshal. Now, they're willing to risk it all to find out if there's more between them than just the law.

movies.title: The Jackal
movies.synopsis: An FBI director works with a Russian agent and a jailed terrorist to hunt down the elusive Jackal, a master-of-disguise assassin on a deadly mission.

movies.title: Focus
movies.synopsis: Nicky, a seasoned master of misdirection, becomes romantically involved with novice con artist Jess. As he's teaching her the tricks of the trade, she gets too close for comfort and he abruptly breaks it off. Three years later, the former flame, now an accomplished femme fatale, shows up in Buenos Aires in the middle of the high-stakes race car circuit. In the midst of Nicky's latest, very dangerous scheme, she throws his plans for a loop and the consummate conman off his game.

movies.title: The Accountant
movies.synopsis: Christian Wolff is a math savant with more affinity for numbers than people. Behind the cover of a small-town CPA office, he works as a freelance accountant for some of the world's most dangerous criminal organisations. With the Treasury Department's Crime Enforcement Division, run by Ray King, starting to close in, Christian takes on a legitimate client: a state-of-the-art robotics company where an accounting clerk has discovered a discrepancy involving millions of dollars. But as Christian 'uncooks' the books and gets closer to the truth, it is the body count that starts to rise.

movies.title: The Hateful Eight
movies.synopsis: In the dead of a Wyoming winter, a bounty hunter and his prisoner find shelter in a cabin currently inhabited by a collection of nefarious characters.

movies.title: Ocean's Eleven
movies.synopsis: Three casinos are the targets for Danny Ocean and his ten partners in crime - the plan is to score the biggest heist in history. The idea is to simultaneously rob the Bellagio, The Mirage, and the MGM Grand casinos in Las Vegas while a huge boxing match is in progress, but it's not long before a SWAT team arrives and a shootout ensues.

movies.title: Ocean's Twelve
movies.synopsis: In this 2004 sequel to Ocean's Eleven, Terry Benedict is still enraged about the millions stolen from his casinos. So to avoid prison time, the team schemes another heist, now in Europe. Benedict tracks Danny down to give them the chance to repay the $160 million in two weeks, and if they agree, he won't have them killed. The team target a rare Faberge egg displayed at a museum in Rome but they discover that a thief, Francois Toulour, is after the same thing.

movies.title: Ocean's Thirteen
movies.synopsis: What are the odds of getting even? Thirteen to one. The 'Con Man' and his boys are back for another heist. This time it's payback. Danny Ocean and the gang would have only one reason to pull of their most ambitious heist - to defend one of their own. When ruthless casino owner Willy Bank double-crosses one of the original Ocean's eleven, Reuben Tishkodd, Danny and the gang team up one more time to see if they can break 'the bank'.

movies.title: Body of Lies
movies.synopsis: The CIA's hunt is on for the mastermind of a wave of terrorist attacks. Roger Ferris is the agency's man on the ground moving from place to place scrambling to stay ahead of ever-shifting events. An eye in the sky a satellite link watches Ferris. At the other end of that real-time link is the CIA's Ed Hoffman strategising events from thousands of miles away. And as Ferris nears the target he discovers trust can be just as dangerous as it is necessary for survival.

movies.title: Edge of Darkness
movies.synopsis: As a homicide detective investigates the death of his daughter, he uncovers not only her secret life, but a corporate cover-up, government collusion and an agent tasked with cleaning up the evidence.

movies.title: The Conjuring
movies.synopsis: Before there was Amityville, there was Harrisville. This film tells the true story of Ed and Lorraine Warren, world-renowned paranormal investigators, who were called to help a family terrorised by a dark presence in a secluded farmhouse. Forced to confront a powerful demonic entity, the Warrens find themselves caught in the most horrifying case of their lives.

movies.title: The Conjuring 2: The Enfield Poltergeist
movies.synopsis: The supernatural demonologists must travel to London to help a single mother and her four children when their house is plagued by malicious spirits.

movies.title: Crime and Punishment in Suburbia
movies.synopsis: A darkly romantic story of murder and redemption, set against an eerily familiar American landscape.

movies.title: Kill Bill Vol. 1
movies.synopsis: Four years after taking a bullet in the head at her own wedding, The Bride emerges from a coma and decides it's time for payback - with a vengeance. Having been gunned down by her former boss, Bill, and his deadly squad of international assassins, it's a kill-or-be-killed fight she didn't start but is determined to finish.

movies.title: Kill Bill Vol. 2
movies.synopsis: The Bride aka Black Mamba former assassin from the Deadly Viper Assassination Squad, having already crossed two names from her Death List, The Bride resumes her quest for justice, taking aim at Budd and Elle Driver, the only survivors from the squad of assassins who betrayed her four years earlier. It's all leading up to the ultimate confrontation with Bill, The Bride's former master and the man who ordered her execution.

movies.title: Zero Dark Thirty
movies.synopsis: For a decade, an elite team of intelligence and military operatives, working in secret across the globe, devoted themselves to a single goal: to find and eliminate Osama bin Laden.

movies.title: Super 8
movies.synopsis: In the summer of 1979, a group of friends in a small Ohio town set out to make a zombie movie. While shooting their Super 8 film, they witness a catastrophic train crash and, after barely escaping themselves, they soon discover that it was not an accident. Shortly after, unusual disappearances and inexplicable events begin to take place in town and local Deputy Jackson Lamb tries to uncover the truth - something more terrifying than any of them could have imagined.

movies.title: Attack the Block
movies.synopsis: From the producers of Shaun of the Dead and Hot Fuzz, this program follows a gang of tough inner-city kids who try to defend their turf against an invasion of savage alien creatures, turning a South London apartment complex into an extraterrestrial war zone.

movies.title: Overlord
movies.synopsis: With only hours until D-Day, a small team of American paratroopers drop into Nazi-occupied France to carry out a mission that's crucial to the invasion's success. These outnumbered G.I.s come face-to-face with enemies unlike any the world has ever seen.

movies.title: 28 Days Later
movies.synopsis: In this zombie-horror update, a powerful virus has escaped from a British research facility and it locks those infected into a permanent state of zombie rage. Jim wakes up alone in a hospital 28 days after the virus has spread throughout the world. Walking through the empty streets, he is attacked by a group of zombies, but he is quickly saved by two human survivors. Jim soon joins with the rest of the survivors, including a band of soldiers, and together they begin their attempts to salvage a future. But will the plague that has infected mankind claim the last human beings?

movies.title: 28 Weeks Later
movies.synopsis: Six months after the Rage Virus has decimated London order has been restored and the war against the infection won, the US Army steps in to help repatriate Mainland Britain. But one of the returning refugees carries a terrible secret that threatens to reignite the deadly explosion of bloodlust, carnage and chaos.

movies.title: Wrong Turn
movies.synopsis: Six teenagers, trapped in the back woods of West Virginia when their cars break down, are hunted down by cannibalistic, inbred mountain men.

movies.title: Sleepwalker
movies.synopsis: Troubled by bouts of sleepwalking and nightmares, graduate student Sarah Foster goes to her university's sleep research centre for help. When she wakes up after her first night of being monitored, the world she lives in seems to have changed in subtle, Twilight-Zone-esque ways. With the help of sleep researcher Scott White, she tries to work her way back to the reality she started in.

movies.title: Premonition
movies.synopsis: Linda Hanson, who has a lovely house, a loving husband and two adorable children. Her life is perfect, until the day she receives the devastating news that her husband Jim has died in a car accident. When she wakes up the next morning to find him alive and well, she assumes it was all a dream, but is shaken by how vivid it was. She soon realises it wasn't a dream, and her world is turned upside down as the surreal circumstances lead her to discover that her perfect life may not have been all that it appeared.

movies.title: Reindeer Games
movies.synopsis: Just released from prison, all Rudy Duncan wants is to start a new life with Ashley, the girl of his dreams, whom he met through pen pal letters in prison. But between them and happiness stands her crazy brother, Gabriel, and his motley crew of deadly criminals who think Rudy has some inside information about a casino where he once had a job, a casino Gabriel and his short-fused posse plan to take down. Now, just as Rudy is beginning his new life, he's caught in a high-velocity avalanche of temptations and surprises that could bury him, unless he can artfully dodge them.

movies.title: The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo
movies.matchTitle: The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo
movies.synopsis: Hoping to distance himself from the fallout of a libel conviction, journalist Mikael Blomkvist retreats to a remote island in Sweden's far north, where the unsolved murder of a young girl still haunts her industrialist uncle 40 years later. Ensconced in a cottage on the island where the killer may still roam, Blomkvist's investigation draws him into the secrets and lies of the rich and powerful, and throws him together with one unlikely ally: tattooed, punk hacker Lisbeth Salander.

movies.title: Savages
movies.synopsis: In a glittering California beach town, two best friends' innovative marijuana business has come to the attention of the ruthless Mexican Baja Cartel. As a seemingly unwinnable war unfolds around them, they're forced to take part in a savage battle of wills to save the girl they both love.

movies.title: The Shallows
movies.synopsis: When a surfer is attacked by a great white shark 20 yards from shore, her short journey back to safety becomes the ultimate contest of wills.

movies.title: Silent Hill
movies.synopsis: Rose is a desperate mother who takes her adopted daughter, Sharon, to the town of Silent Hill in an attempt to cure her of her ailment. After a violent car crash, Sharon disappears and Rose begins her desperate search to get her back. She descends into a fog of smouldering ash and into the centre of the twisted reality of a town's terrible secret. Pursued by grotesquely deformed creatures and a townspeople stuck in permanent purgatory, Rose begins to uncover the truth behind the apocalyptic disaster that burnt the town 30 years back. Dare to step inside the horrific town of Silent Hill, where darkness preys on every soul and Hell's creations await around every corner, but know that once you enter, there is no turning back.

movies.title: The Silence of the Lambs
movies.synopsis: A psychopath nicknamed Buffalo Bill is murdering women across the Midwest. Believing it takes one to know one, the FBI sends Agent Clarice Starling to interview a demented prisoner who may provide clues to the killer's actions. That prisoner is psychiatrist Dr Hannibal Lecter, a brilliant, diabolical cannibal who agrees to help Starling only if she'll feed his morbid curiosity with details of her own complicated life. As their relationship develops, Starling is forced to confront not only her own hidden demons, but also an evil so powerful that she may not have the courage - or strength - to stop it!

movies.title: From Dusk Till Dawn
movies.synopsis: Brothers and convicts Seth and Ritchie Gecko are two robbing and murdering thugs on their way to Mexico to deliver a large amount of cash. The problem is after killing so many people, the cops and Feds are hot on their heels and the Gecko brothers need a way across the border. Luckily for them they encounter (and kidnap) the Fuller family. Disgruntled father and former preacher Jacob and his kids Kate and Jacob are heading to Mexico to get away from it all after the death of their mother. Arriving at their Mexican destination, a biker bar in the middle of nowhere, they settle in and wait for their contact to arrive. Unfortunately the bar is also a vampire hangout and soon the Geckos and Fullers are fighting for their lives with the help of other interesting characters such as Sex Machine and Frost.

movies.title: Jeepers Creepers 2
movies.synopsis: As its 23 horrifying days of flesh-eating come to an end, an ancient creature known as the Creeper embarks on a final voracious feeding frenzy, terrorising a group of varsity basketball players, cheerleaders, and coaches stranded on a remote highway after their bus breaks down. Fighting their own fears and prejudices while trapped aboard the isolated bus, the terrified group of young athletes are forced to come together and do battle against the winged creature hell bent on completing its grizzly ritual of feasting on humans.

movies.title: Mad Mom
movies.synopsis: Amber Vickers is ecstatic that she will finally be making the walk down the aisle with her prince charming Luke. After multiple failed relationships, she was beginning to think that something was wrong; but her soon-to-be mother-in-law and best friend, Jill, believes that Amber is the picture-perfect daughter she never had. Everything is coming up roses until Sharon Vickers, Amber's mother, arrives for a visit. Gaudy, straight-laced and opinionated, Sharon is the complete opposite of Jill. What was supposed to be a benign first meeting of the in-law's quickly turns into a competition, as Sharon and Jill have widely differing views on life, love and marriage. As the weekend visit is coming to an end, Sharon takes matters into her own hands, rendering Jill incapable of escaping her house, and proving to her once and for all that no one comes between Sharon and her daughter.

movies.title: Man on a Ledge
movies.synopsis: An ex-cop turned con threatens to jump to his death from a Manhattan hotel rooftop. The NYPD officer responds to a screaming women and calls dispatch. NYPD then dispatches a female police psychologist to talk him down. However, unbeknown to the police on the scene, the suicide attempt is a cover for the biggest diamond heist ever pulled.

movies.title: The Mothman Prophecies
movies.synopsis: John Klein is a reporter whose life is wrecked when his wife, Mary, dies suddenly. Two years later, en route to an assignment, he inexplicably finds himself 640km out of his way in Point Pleasant, West Virginia, a small town in the grip of mass hysteria, apparently caused by sightings of a red-eyed, winged creature dubbed the 'Mothman'. Since Mary died drawing precisely the same creature, Klein is very curious to delve into the mystery. Ignoring the advice of the local sheriff, he begins his quest, not realising that his own sanity could be in jeopardy.

movies.title: Bridge of Spies
movies.synopsis: James Donovan is a Brooklyn lawyer who finds himself thrust into the centre of the Cold War when the CIA sends him on the near-impossible task to negotiate the release of a captured American U-2 pilot. A story inspired by true events that captures the essence of a man who risked everything and vividly brings his personal journey to life.

movies.title: Blood Diamond
movies.synopsis: Set against the backdrop of civil war and chaos in 1990s Sierra Leone, this film tells the story of Danny Archer, a South African mercenary, and Solomon Vandy, a Mende fisherman. Both men are African, but their histories are as different as can be, until their fates become joined in a common quest to recover a rare pink diamond that can transform their lives. With the help of Maddy Bowen, an American journalist whose idealism is tempered by a deepening connection with Archer, the two men embark on a trek through rebel territory a journey that could save Solomon's family and give Archer the second chance he thought he would never have.

movies.title: Panic Room
movies.synopsis: A mother and daughter move into a home with an impregnable 'panic' room. When three thieves break in, they are trapped there in a terrifying battle of wits.

movies.title: Solaris
movies.synopsis: A psychologist investigates mysterious happenings aboard a space station whose crew is acting strangely after exposure to the mysterious planet Solaris.

movies.title: Twisted Sisters
movies.synopsis: Presided over by Daisy, the chapter's dazzling president, Psi Kaps are the queens of the campus. Sarah becomes Daisy's favourite pledge and is taken under her wing, allowing her to see how the sorority is run more like a ruthless business than a sisterhood. The girls maintain saintly appearances while promoting cut-throat seduction and destruction behind the scenes. Everything from the student body through administration is controlled with bribes and blackmail, and Sarah can't help but watch in horror as her world starts to crumble around her. Is she strong enough to take down Daisy and the house she's built? Or will she come to understand the true meaning of the sorority motto: Psi Kap for life, Psi Kap 'til death.

movies.title: Se7en
movies.synopsis: Two cops track a brilliant and elusive killer who orchestrates a string of horrific murders, each kill targeting a practitioner of one of the seven deadly sins. A physical, mental and spiritual thriller with a sure understanding of what terrifies us.

movies.title: The Town
movies.synopsis: A bank robber falls in love with a former robbery hostage and decides he wants out of the life. With the Feds closing in he must choose: betray his friends or lose the woman he loves.

movies.title: Betrayed By Lies
movies.synopsis: When Sabrina suspects her husband of possible infidelity, she discovers he has another wife and reveals illegal business dealings with his father-in-law. Now it is not only her marriage that is on the line, but her life.

movies.title: Lost Junction
movies.synopsis: A woman suspected of killing her husband runs off with his money to New Orleans. She falls in love with a man who also has a dark past, and they hatch a plan to clear her name.

movies.title: Gold
movies.synopsis: The epic true tale of one man's pursuit of the American Dream: to discover gold. A prospector desperate for a lucky break teams up with a similarly eager geologist and sets off on an amazing journey to find gold in the uncharted jungle of Indonesia. Getting the gold was hard, but keeping it will be even harder, sparking an adventure through the most powerful boardrooms of Wall Street.

movies.title: Red Riding Hood
movies.synopsis: For years the villagers of Daggerhorn have maintained an uneasy truce with a werewolf - but the beast changes the stakes by killing the older sister of brave young Valerie. Promised in marriage to one man but in love with another, Valerie is affected yet again by the creature's bloody actions. When a werewolf hunter warns that the beast takes human form by day and walks among them, panic sets in as the death toll rises. And Valerie learns she has a unique connection to the wolf that inexorably draws them together, making her both suspect and bait.

movies.title: Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows
movies.matchTitle: Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows
movies.synopsis: Sherlock Holmes and Dr Watson attempt to outwit their fiercest adversary ever, Professor Moriarty.

movies.title: Pulp Fiction
movies.synopsis: Winnfield and Vincent Vega are two hitmen out to retrieve a suitcase stolen from their employer, mob boss Marcellus Wallace. Wallace has also asked Vincent to take his wife Mia out a few days later when Wallace himself will be out of town. Butch Coolidge is an ageing boxer who is paid by Wallace to lose his next fight. Honey Bunny and Pumpkin are a couple of young lovers and small time thieves who decide they need a change of venue. The lives of these seemingly unrelated people are woven together in a wildly entertaining and exhilarating motion picture adventure that both thrills and amuses.

movies.title: District 9
movies.synopsis: With stunning special effects and gritty realism, the film plunges us into a world where the aliens have landed, only to be exiled to a slum on the fringes of Johannesburg. Now, one lone human discovers the mysterious secret of the extra-terrestrial weapon technology. Hunted and hounded through the bizarre back alleys of an alien shantytown, he will discover what it means to be the ultimate outsider on your own planet.

movies.title: The Descent
movies.synopsis: On an annual extreme outdoor adventure, six women meet in a remote part of the Appalachians to explore a cave hidden deep in the woods. Far below the surface of the earth, disaster strikes when a rock fall blocks their exit and there's no way out. The women push on, praying for another exit, but there is something else lurking under the earth. The friends are now prey, forced to unleash their most primal instincts in an all-out war against an unspeakable horror - one that attacks without warning, again and again and again.

movies.title: The Descent: Part 2
movies.synopsis: In this sequel to the critically acclaimed horror hit a dazed, bloodied and speechless Sarah emerges alone from the Appalachian cave system, before being forced back underground to help the rescue team find her missing friends. As the team move deeper into the caves, Sarah's flashes of fractured memory intensify and she begins to realise the full horror of the would-be rescue mission. Only Sarah knows the terror which lurks in the shadows of the caves. They are about to encounter a new tribe of Crawlers, inbred, deformed and even more viciously feral than those Sarah faced before.

movies.title: The Others
movies.synopsis: While awaiting her husband's return from war, Grace and her two young children live an unusually isolated existence behind the locked doors and drawn curtains of a secluded island mansion. When three mysterious servants arrive, it becomes frighteningly clear that there is far more to this house than meets the eye. In order to discover the truth, Grace must abandon all of her fears and beliefs and enter the otherworldly heart of the supernatural.

movies.title: Event Horizon
movies.synopsis: A sci-fi thriller about a rescue mission to an abandoned spaceship that turns out to be a close encounter of the most evil kind.

movies.title: Monster-In-Law
movies.synopsis: After years of looking for Mr. Right, Charlotte 'Charlie' Cantilini finally finds the man of her dreams only to discover that his mother, Viola, is the woman of her nightmares. A recently-fired national news anchor who is afraid she will lose her son the way she has just lost her career, Viola does everything she can to scare off her son's new fiance by becoming the world's worst mother-in-law. While Viola's long-time assistant Ruby does her best to help Viola execute her crazy schemes, Charlie decides to fight back and the gloves come off as the women battle it out to see just who the alpha-female is.

movies.title: Wimbledon
movies.synopsis: Pro tennis "hot shot" Lizzie Bradbury is a rising star who lives to win. But when she falls for long-shot contender Peter Colt amid the glitz and glamour of Wimbledon, Lizzie discovers it's not if you win or lose, but how you play the game ... of love. A deliciously witty romantic comedy about chasing your dreams and risking your heart, this filmis a fun and charming story of love across the net.

movies.title: Fool's Gold
movies.synopsis: Ben Finn Finnegan is an affable, modern-day treasure hunter who is obsessed with finding the legendary 18th century Queens Dowry 40 chests of priceless treasure that was lost at sea in 1715. In his quest, Finn has sunk everything he has, including his marriage to Tess Finnegan. Just as Tess has begun to rebuild her life, working aboard a mega-yacht owned by billionaire Nigel Honeycutt, Finn discovers a vital clue to the treasures whereabouts. Much to Tess' consternation, Finn manoeuvres himself aboard Nigel's yacht and, using his roguish charm, convinces the tycoon and his daughter, Gemma, to join him in the pursuit of the Spanish treasure. But they are not the only ones after the prize. Finn's one-time mentor, Moe Fitch, and a ruthless local gangster are intent on beating Finn to the prize. Let the treasure hunt begin.

movies.title: What Men Want
movies.synopsis: A successful sports agent mysteriously gains the ability to hear men's thoughts. With this newfound power, she looks to outsmart her colleagues, but the lengths she goes to put her relationships to the test in this hilarious comedy!

movies.title: The Ghosts of Girlfriends Past
movies.synopsis: Connor Mead is the kind of guy who dumps three girlfriends. At the same time. By teleconference. So when he attends his brother's wedding he has a single goal: score with the only bridesmaid he somehow missed. But the ghost of his departed Uncle Wayne -who taught him to love 'em and leave 'em - has another goal in mind: restore Connor's lost faith in true love, a tough assignment requiring the services of many, many Ghosts of Girlfriends Past.

movies.title: Life As We Know It
movies.synopsis: A mismatched couple must overcome their dislike for each other when they unexpectedly find themselves caring for an orphaned child.

movies.title: Never Been Kissed
movies.synopsis: Josie Geller is a bright 25-year-old copy editor at Chicago's revered newspaper, The Chicago Sun-Times, who wants more out of life and yearns to be a reporter. Josie is skilled at her profession, but completely clueless in her personal life. She was a brainy nerd in high school, a geek to the core, and she has never had a serious relationship with a man, not even a proper kiss, much to her chagrin. But things are about to change for Josie when her dream to become a reporter becomes a reality. Josie's first assignment couldn't be more nightmarish: she must go undercover at a local high school to report on modern teenagers. Now, eight years senior to the oldest pupil in the class, Josie must figure out her story and a potential new love, teacher Sam Coulson, while reliving her horrific adolescence.

movies.title: Must Love Dogs
movies.synopsis: A vulnerable, newly divorced pre-school teacher gets roped into the online dating scene by her well-meaning sister. The search for Mr Right turns hilarious.

movies.title: The Prince & Me: The Royal Wedding
movies.matchTitle: The Prince & Me 2: The Royal Wedding
movies.synopsis: Edvard and Paige are just weeks away from the big day. All is proceeding according to plan, until a conniving royal named Albert finds a centuries-old Danish law that forbids the ascension to king if the prince were to marry a non-royal, which Paige is certainly not. To "help out" in the matter, Albert offers a solution in the form of his own daughter, Princess Kirsten, a childhood friend of Edvard's that has blossomed into an attractive and graceful adult. The Danish tabloids are swarming for juicy gossip, setting forth a chain of events that threatens to make Edvard have to choose between his kingdom and his heart.

movies.title: Becoming Jane
movies.synopsis: This film introduces us to a 20-year-old Jane Austen - highly unconventional and perilously close to old maid status by 18th century England standards. We also meet many of the people in her world that would later shape characters in her celebrated novels. Among them is roguish Irishman, Tom Lefroy, the man with whom she has a passionate but unapproved love affair. These are the formative years that that would lay the foundation for her career as one of the world's greatest romantic writers.

movies.title: Mamma Mia!
movies.synopsis: Sophie has just one wish to make her wedding perfect: to have her father walk her down the aisle. Now she just has to find out who he is. Join the music, laughter and fun of the irresistibly charming musical celebration of mothers, daughters and fathers, and true loves lost and new ones found. Based on the Broadway smash-hit and filled with the ABBA songs you know and love, it's the feel-good experience that will have you singing and dancing over and over again.

movies.title: Sliding Doors
movies.synopsis: A young woman's love life and career both hinge, unknown to her, on whether or not she catches a morning train back to her apartment. Two wholly different universes unfold about alternate realities, the reliability of subway schedules and the role fate plays in shaping random lives.

movies.title: Crazy, Stupid, Love.
movies.synopsis: After his wife Emily's confession that she had a fling with her co-worker David and that she wants a divorce, Cal starts to haunt his local bar, devastated at his situation. He observes a handsome young womaniser, Jacob, in action as he lays slick moves on various young ladies, but is surprised when Jacob notices his incessant sad-sack rantings. Jacob offers to help Cal get back in the dating game, and Cal is astonished when the combination of an image makeover and some smart tips actually work.

movies.title: Four Weddings and a Funeral
movies.synopsis: The champagne is flowing - and so is the fun - in this romantic comedy about two people who belong together but just can't seem to tie the knot. Charlie is always the best man but never the groom. Determined to avoid even a hint of commitment, this handsome English gentleman is notoriously late to every wedding. But today he's in for a real surprise because not only did he forget the ring ... but he also just caught a glimpse of the girl of his dreams!

movies.title: Nine Months
movies.synopsis: In this hilarious comedy about a pregnancy, parenthood and panic, Sam has it all: a wonderful girlfriend, a successful child psychology business, and a red Porsche. But all that changes when his girlfriend tells him she's pregnant. Torn between advice from an overbearing couple, his bachelor buddy, and a crazy Russian gynaecologist, Sam's got nine months to grow up - or risk losing it all.

movies.title: Notting Hill
movies.synopsis: Anna Scott is the world's most famous movie star. Her picture has been plastered on the cover of every magazine, and every time she makes a movie, the entire world knows about it. William Thacker owns a travel bookstore in the quaint neighbourhood of Notting Hill. His business is stagnant, he has the roommate from hell and his love life is completely non-existent. Then one day, their paths cross and the couple comes to face the ultimate question: can two people fall in love with the whole world watching?

movies.title: About a Boy
movies.synopsis: Will Lightman is a good-looking, smooth-talking bachelor whose primary goal in life is avoiding any kind of responsibility. But when he invents an imaginary son in order to meet attractive single mums, Will gets a hilarious lesson about life from a bright, but hopelessly geeky 12-year-old named Marcus. Now, as Will struggles to teach Marcus the art of being cool, Marcus teaches Will that you're never too old to grow up.

movies.title: Two Weeks Notice
movies.synopsis: Lucy Kelton is a top-flight attorney who has risen to the position of chief legal counsel for one of New York's leading commercial real estate firms, the Wade Corporation. However, Lucy's job has one significant drawback - George Wade, the eccentric and remarkably self-centred head of the firm. George seems entirely incapable of making a decision without Lucy's advice, whether it actually involves a legal matter or not, and while she's fond of George, being at his beck and call 24 hours a day has brought her to the end of her rope.

movies.title: Love Actually
movies.synopsis: Love's causing chaos all over London. Even the PM is smitten. Ten separate stories intertwine in a Christmas Eve climax.

movies.title: Sex and the City
movies.synopsis: Carrie Bradshaw, successful author and everyone's favourite fashion icon-next-door, is back, her famously sardonic wit intact and sharper than ever, as she continues to narrate her own story about sex, love and the fashion-obsessed single woman in New York City. Sex and the City finds Carrie, Samantha, Charlotte, and Miranda four years after the hit series ended, as our favourite friends continue to juggle jobs and relationships while navigating motherhood, marriage and Manhattan real estate.

movies.title: The Romantics
movies.synopsis: Alliances are tested when seven college friends reunite to watch two of their group get married at a seaside wedding. But the maid of honour and the groom share a passionate history and the bride isn't the only one who is wondering if it is all in the past.

movies.title: When Sparks Fly
movies.synopsis: Hank is planning to propose to longtime girlfriend Amy, but before he has the chance to ask, she announces she has been offered a dream job in Chicago. Hank realizes that a long distance relationship won't work for them and they go their separate ways. Seven years later, Amy returns to her hometown and learns that her best friend, Sammie, is marrying Hank. As Amy helps Sammie in the wedding planning it becomes evident that Amy and Hank still have feelings for each other. Sparks fly when she rekindles an old flame and discovers that the life and love she left behind are exactly what she has been missing.

movies.title: Paper Towns
movies.synopsis: This coming-of-age story centres on Quentin and his enigmatic neighbour Margo, who loved mysteries so much she became one. After taking him on an all-night adventure through their hometown, Margo suddenly disappears, leaving behind cryptic clues for Quentin to decipher. The search leads Quentin and his quick-witted friends on an exhilarating adventure that is equal parts hilarious and moving. Ultimately, to track down Margo, Quentin must find a deeper understanding of true friendship, and true love.

movies.title: Nobody's Fool
movies.synopsis: Tiffany Haddish (Girls Trip) is hysterical in Tyler Perry's (Madea) most outrageous comedy yet. Trying to get back on her feet, wild child Tanya (Haddish) looks to her buttoned-up sister Danica (Tika Sumpter, Ride Along) to get her life together. As these polar opposites hilariously collide, Tanya discovers that Danica's picture-perfect life - including her online romance - may not be what it seems. With the aid of her eccentric mother (comedy legend Whoopi Goldberg), Tanya will do whatever it takes to help... even if it means completely blowing up her sister's life! Omari Hardwick (Power) and Amber Riley (Glee) also star in this side-splittingly funny hit.

movies.title: French Kiss
movies.synopsis: Kate and fiance Charlie seem set for a predictable future life together in Canada - until Charlie attends a seminar in Paris and falls for heavenly Juliette. Juliette is beautiful and French. Kate decides to follow and win back what is hers in a straight fight between good old American know-how and the ageless savoir-faire of Europe. That's when Luc appears on the scene. Luc is handsome and French, and more than happy to instruct Kate in some of the finer points of seduction.

movies.title: Mean Girls 2
movies.synopsis: Jo Mitchell (Meaghan Martin) is the daughter of a NASCAR mechanic (Linden Ashby), who is spending her senior year at North Shore High, her sixth school in four years. Jo normally keeps to herself, but when she stands up to three girls who rule the school - queen bee Mandi (Maiara Walsh), sexpot Chastity (Claire Holt), and well-dressed germaphobe Hope (Nicole Gale Anderson) - she finds herself the target of their mean-girl games. Confusing matters is the class' wealthy wallflower, Abby (Jennifer Stone), whose rich father offers Jo college tuition in exchange for befriending Abby. Jo accepts the deal and winds up becoming best friends with Abby, falling for Mandi's stepbrother Tyler (Diego Gonzalez Boneta) and eventually taking on the mean girls and their control of the school.

movies.title: Footloose
movies.synopsis: In this remake of the 1984 classic, big city teen Ren McCormack moves to a quiet little town and discovers that the hard-line minister has outlawed loud music and dancing. But everything changes when Ren decides to challenge the ban, revitalising the town and falling in love with the minister's rebellious daughter Ariel. So get ready to cut loose.

movies.title: Forces of Nature
movies.synopsis: Ben is travelling to Savannah for his upcoming wedding to Bridget. On take-off his plane suffers an accident. Now terrified of flying, he agrees to travel with the free-spirited Sarah who also needs to get to Savannah.

movies.title: Bewitched
movies.synopsis: To revive his flagging career, actor Jack Wyatt sets out to make an updated version of the classic sitcom Bewitched. But he unknowingly casts a real witch as his wife.

movies.title: Stuck In Love
movies.synopsis: Three years past his divorce, veteran novelist Bill Borgens can't stop obsessing over, let alone spying on, his ex-wife Erica, who ignominiously left him for another man. Even as his neighbour-with-benefits, Tricia tries to push him back into the dating pool, he remains blind to anyone else's charms. Meanwhile, his fiercely independent collegiate daughter Samantha is publishing her first novel while recoiling at the very thought of first love with a diehard romantic; and his teen son Rusty is trying to find his voice, both as a fantasy writer and as the unexpected boyfriend of a dream girl with unsettlingly real problems. As each of these situations mounts into a tangled trio of romantic holiday crises, it brings the Borgens to surprising revelations about how endings become beginnings.

movies.title: Friends with Benefits
movies.synopsis: Justin Timberlake and Mila Kunis star as best friends who are both coming out of disastrous relationships. They decide to make a 'friends with benefits' pact vowing to stop the casual sex if either become emotionally attached. While the set-up works at first, soon the two friends fall in love and must re-evaluate what they mean to each other.

movies.title: Hitch
movies.synopsis: Hitch is a cocky and successful date doctor for the unlucky in love. But when he falls for gossip columnist Sara, he forgets his own rules.

movies.title: Sex and the City 2
movies.synopsis: The fun, the fashion, the friendship. Carrie, Samantha, Charlotte and Miranda come together to take another bite out of the Big Apple - and beyond. What happens after you say "I do"? Life is everything the ladies ever wished it would be, but it wouldn't be Sex and the City if life didn't hold a few more surprises. After all, sometimes you just have to get away with the girls.

movies.title: The Prince & Me
movies.synopsis: Paige Morgan is on the fast track to creating the life she's always wanted. What she never counted on was meeting Eddie, a disarming stranger who happens to also be the Crown Prince of Denmark! She grew up on a farm and drives her dad's pickup. He grew up in a royal palace and takes the Queen's limo out for a spin when bored with his Lamborghini. They come from two different worlds but there's an undeniable attraction and Paige must choose between staying with her Prince or following her own aspirations. Can she find a way to have it all?

movies.title: Save the Last Dance
movies.synopsis: Sara is a small-town girl with a big dream: to become a world-class ballerina. But when her mother suddenly dies, Sara must abandon her plans and join her estranged father on Chicago's gritty South Side. A white girl in a predominantely black neighbourhood, Sara feels out of place - until she is befriended by a black classmate, Chenille, and her handsome brother, Derek. Sparks fly between Sara and Derek, whose shared loved for dance leads to romance. But as Sara and Derek's relationship grows, so does opposition from their families and friends. Now Sara and Derek face the biggest challenge of their young lives - to stay true to their dreams ... and each other.

movies.title: At First Sight
movies.synopsis: A poignant love story that follows a young woman who falls in love with a blind man. When she encourages him to undergo a radical operation to restore his sight, he ultimately finds his truest vision comes from the love he finds in his heart.

movies.title: Eat Pray Love
movies.synopsis: Believing there's more to life than a husband, house and career, Liz Gilbert finds herself with a new appetite for life. She leaves New York and embarks on a yearlong journey, traveling to Italy, India and Bali, seeking self-discovery through good food, meditation and the prospect of finding true love.

movies.title: Larry Crowne
movies.synopsis: A romantic and optimistic comedy about how it's never too late to reinvent yourself. When he suddenly finds himself without his long-standing blue-collar job, Larry Crowne enrols at his local college to start over. There, he becomes part of an eclectic community of students and develops a crush on his teacher. Now this simple guy will discover that when you think everything worth having has passed you by, you just might find your reason to live.

movies.title: Blended
movies.synopsis: After a terrible blind date, two single parents and their kids find themselves stuck together on an African wildlife holiday where things go from bad to worse.

movies.title: The Ugly Truth
movies.synopsis: In this wildly funny battle of the sexes, Abby, a successful morning show producer, is looking for a lot in a man. Mike, her obnoxious TV star, knows men only want one thing. Determined to prove that she's not romantically challenged, Abby takes Mike's advice during a promising new romance, but the unexpected results will stun everyone.

movies.title: One Fine Day
movies.synopsis: Melanie Parker is a career-minded architect and supermum, taking on the demands of single parenting in New York City. Jack Taylor is a hard-driving newspaper columnist and every-other-weekend dad, challenging the improprieties of City Hall. Having been let down in the past, Melanie has almost given up on men, except for the adorable five-year-old who calls her mummy, and Jack thinks that women are just fine, as long as they keep their emotional distance. When they are inadvertently thrown together for one chaotic day, the only thing they have in common are identical cellular phones. The last thing they need is to get involved with each other's lives, jobs and kids. The last thing they expect to feel is an attraction. But the next thing they know, they're falling in love.

movies.title: Woman on Top
movies.synopsis: Isabella is a gorgeous chef who melts the palates and hearts of men everywhere. When Isabella decides to break free from her rocky marriage and move to San Francisco, she discovers the perfect recipe for coming out on top - her own cooking show. But when her producer falls in love and her ex-husband comes to town, who knows which man will end up on bottom? Filled with passion and laughter, this film is a spicy comedy about making relationships more delicious.

movies.title: For Love Of The Game
movies.synopsis: When a legendary pitcher strikes out with his girlfriend, he has to play the game of his life. The suspense lasts until the last ball is thrown in this heartwarming drama.

movies.title: Maid in Manhattan
movies.synopsis: Marisa Ventura is a struggling single mum who works at a posh Manhattan hotel and dreams of a better life for her and her young son. One fateful day, hotel guest and senatorial candidate Christopher Marshall meets Marisa and mistakes her for a wealthy socialite. After an enchanting evening together, the two fall madly in love. But when Marisa's true identity is revealed, issues of class and social status threaten to separate them. Can two people from very different worlds overcome their differences and live happily ever after?

movies.title: Rumour Has It
movies.synopsis: A woman, nervous about her upcoming wedding, discovers a dynamite family secret that goes to the heart of her trepidation.

movies.title: When a Man Loves a Woman
movies.matchTitle: When a Man Loves a Woman
movies.synopsis: Alice and Michael Green are a passionate couple who have worked hard to build a good life for themselves and their two young daughters. But a dark secret from Alice's past is about to surface - a secret that threatens to destroy them as lovers, as a family, and as individuals. A story of fiery passion and the enduring power of love.

movies.title: The Prince & Me: Royal Honeymoon
movies.matchTitle: The Prince & Me: A Royal Honeymoon
movies.synopsis: King Edvard is sick of going through the affairs of State with his chief of staff Soren because all he wants to do is go on his honeymoon with his new Queen Paige. Paige is mostly involved with charities that she has taken on. At the airport the sinister figure of Edvard's chief opponent in the government, Prime Minster John Polonius has a present for the queen; an old book on royal protocol. He obviously doesn't think she's Queen material and he is appalled at her plans to start working as a doctor. Polonius also has plans to secure oil rights for the North Country to make a killing in opposition of the King's wishes and there's an old boyfriend of Paige who upsets the apple cart. Scott even ends up in a sword duel with the King.

movies.title: The Jane Austen Book Club
movies.synopsis: Six months. Six novels. Six members. The Jane Austen Book Club takes reading the classics to new heights of passion. When five women and one man get together to discuss the English writer's beloved novels, they realise the heartaches of Emma, Mr Darcy and the Bennet sisters are not so different from their own. Finding comfort, wit and wisdom from the pages and each other, they discover that, in matters of love, all they need to ask is: what would Jane do?

movies.title: Ruby Sparks
movies.synopsis: Calvin (Paul Dano) is a young novelist who achieved phenomenal success early in his career but is now struggling with his writing - as well as his romantic life. Finally, he makes a breakthrough and creates a character named Ruby who inspires him. When Calvin finds Ruby (Zoe Kazan), in the flesh, sitting on his couch about a week later, he is completely flabbergasted that his words have turned into a living, breathing person.

movies.title: Elizabethtown
movies.synopsis: This film follows the story of Drew Baylor, a man down on his luck, as he journeys to his roots in small-town Kentucky to bury his father. Drew finds new life in his interactions with his colourful extended family and in his unexpected romance with Claire, a quirky and persistent airline stewardess.

movies.title: No Strings Attached
movies.synopsis: Emma and Adam are life-long friends who almost ruin everything by having sex one morning. In order to protect their friendship, they make a pact to keep their relationship strictly "no strings attached." "No strings" means no jealousy, no expectations, no fighting, no flowers, no baby voices. It means they can do whatever they want, whenever they want, in whatever public place they want, as long as they don't fall in love. The questions become - Can you have sex without love getting in the way? And can their friendship survive?

movies.title: The Vow
movies.synopsis: A newlywed couple recovers from a car accident that puts the wife in a coma. Waking up with severe memory loss, her husband endeavours to win her heart again.

movies.title: Kate & Leopold
movies.synopsis: Kate McKay is a modern female executive in New York City whose drive to succeed in the cutthroat corporate world has left little time for romance. When her genius ex-boyfriend discovers a portal to travel through time, and brings back a 19th-century nobleman named Leopold to prove it, a sceptical Kate reluctantly takes responsibility for showing Leopold the 21st century.

movies.title: Definitely, Maybe
movies.synopsis: Will is a father who decides to tell his daughter the story of how he met her mother, when she starts asking questions about sex and relationships. Will discovers that a second look at the past might also give him a second chance at the future. It's definitely never too late to go back and maybe find a happy ending.

movies.title: Dear John
movies.synopsis: Tells the story of John Tyree, a young solider home on leave, and Savannah Curtis, the idealistic college student he falls in love with during her spring vacation.

movies.title: New Year's Eve
movies.synopsis: A romantic comedy which follows the interlinked stories of several New Yorkers in the lead up to the biggest night of the year. As the build-up begins to the excitement of New Years Eve in New York City, record company secretary Ingrid resigns from her job impulsively after a near accident, but offers courier Paul her tickets to the exclusive Ahern Records New Years Eve ball if he helps her to complete a list of resolutions. Meanwhile, Pauls sister Kim struggles with the growing independence of her teenage daughter Hailey, while his friend Randy is stuck in a broken elevator with singer Elise, who is due to perform at the ball. With time slipping away from the old year, its impact is keenly felt in a hospital, where two couples compete to have the first baby after midnight, and a dying man is comforted by a sympathetic nurse.

movies.title: She's the One
movies.synopsis: A funny and wry romantic comedy about two brothers wrestling with their preposterous approaches to life and love. Mickey, a free-spirited New York cabbie, and Francis, a materialistic Wall Street stockbroker, are extremely competitive and confused about women as a result of their father's influence. Though they disagree about nearly everything, they have one thing in common: Mickey's ex-fiancee Heather is Francis's secret lover. Though both brothers have beautiful wives, Heather triggers their long-time sibling rivalry with uproarious and unexpected results.

movies.title: The Prince & Me: Elephant Adventure
movies.matchTitle: The Prince & Me 4: The Elephant Adventure
movies.synopsis: One year after their royal wedding, the beautiful young king and queen of Denmark are invited to the wedding of Princess Myra, the only daughter of King Saryu of Sangyoon. They set off for distant Asia not realising they're about to have the adventure of their lives.

movies.title: Road Less Traveled
movies.synopsis: Country music singer Charlotte comes back home to Tennessee a week before she's set to get married, hoping to borrow her late mother's wedding dress from her grandmother. But when she runs into her high school sweetheart, Ray, sparks begin to fly.

movies.title: Five Feet Apart
movies.synopsis: When Life Keeps You Apart, Fight For Every Inch.

movies.title: What Women Want
movies.synopsis: Nick, a somewhat chauvinistic advertising exec hot shot, has his life turned haywire when a fluke accident enables him to hear what women think. At first all he wants to do is rid himself of this curse, until a wacky psychologist shows him that this could be used to his advantage! His first target is Darcy McGuire, the very woman that got the promotion he wanted. But just as his plan is beginning to work, love gets in the way.

movies.title: 40 Days and 40 Nights
movies.synopsis: On the heels of a disastrous breakup and a string of unfulfilling romantic conquests, Matt Sullivan yearns to become a better, more complete person. In the midst of his despair, he chooses to test himself by making a vow of no sex whatsoever for 40 days and 40 nights. With all his friends betting he won't make it and a seductive new girl in his life, it's all Matt can do to just hold on.

movies.title: New in Town
movies.synopsis: Lucy Hill is a high-powered executive in love with her upscale Miami lifestyle. Seeking a big promotion, Lucy agrees to move to a remote Minnesota town to oversee the restructuring of a manufacturing plant. Enduring icy roads, freezing weather and a chilly reception from the locals, this is Lucy's toughest assignment. How will she ever win over the union representative Ted Mitchell and the frosty township, as well as do her job?

movies.title: Mother's Day
movies.synopsis: An emotional tribute of interwoven stories about a group of women with one important thing in common: mothers. A celebration of mothers everywhere, enjoy the laughter, tears and love as three generations come together in the week leading up to Mother's Day.

movies.title: The Switch
movies.synopsis: An offbeat comedy about Kassie, a smart, fun-loving single woman who, despite her slightly neurotic best friend Wally's objections, decides it's time to have a baby even if it means doing it by herself with a little help from a charming sperm donor. But, unbeknownst to her, Kassie's plans go awry because of a last minute switch that isn't discovered until seven years later when Wally finally gets acquainted with Kassie's precocious though slightly neurotic son.

movies.title: Legends of the Fall
movies.synopsis: An epic tale, set in the Rocky Mountains of Montana in the early 1900s, of three brothers and their father living in the remote wilderness and how their lives are affected by love, betrayal and brotherhood. After being discharged, Colonel Ludlow decides to raise his three sons in the wilds of Montana, where they can grow up away from the government and society he has learned to despise. As the brothers set out to fight a war in Europe, suspicion and jealousy threatens to tear apart their once indestructible bond when Susanna enters their lives.

movies.title: Playing It Cool
movies.synopsis: A fresh, quirky, and weirdly relatable story about Me, a young screenwriter disillusioned by love. He meets a breathtaking young woman, Her, at a charity dinner by pretending to be a philanthropist. Only one problem... she's engaged. With his agent chasing him for a screenplay about love, and against the better advice of his best friend Scott, our young hero enters into a platonic relationship to be able to keep seeing Her. This is a story of love and quarter-life crisis amidst figuring out who you are and what your destiny holds.

movies.title: You've Got Mail
movies.synopsis: Two anonymous e-mailers fall head-over-laptops in love, unaware they are fierce rivals in the bookshop business.

movies.title: Serendipity
movies.synopsis: In the course of one magical evening, Jonathan and Sara meet unexpectedly, but part when she decides that fate must determine their future.
